        hpcom:BookSciFi ;
    schema:name "Revelation Space" ;
    schema:review "An expansive space opera that promises big mysteries - and delivers! There are some rought edges, and the novel feels a little too big for the story and a little too slow for what you would want the pace to be - but nothing is wasted and there is no dull moment. The ending and the world building made me get all the other three books as I know Reynolds has big ideas and delivers them with great details."@en ;
