    schema:review "Vicious, gory, disturbing tribal stories where people can morph into animals and completely uppend any notion of civilisation. I was okay with the violent aspects of the story, but the writing style and the overuse of descriptions did not make it easy to understand what was going on. The story itself wasn't interesting to me."@en ;
    schema:url "https://harshp.com/hobbies/books/697"^^xsd:anyURI .

