    schema:name "The Name of the Rose" ;
    schema:review "Sherlock Holmes set in Medieval Italy with lots of excellent discussions and discourses on religion and philosophy. This was a really nice read, and I could see the emerging blossom that eventually became Foucault's Pendulum."@en ;
