        hpcom:BookSciFi ;
    schema:name "Bear Head" ;
    schema:review "I enjoyed Dogs of War because it had something different, but was annoyed with its anthromorphic storyline and characterisation. This is a sequel with the same outlines, though as a more techno-oriented thriller. It was okay, I read it because I was sitting in an airport and wanted to get this book out of the way."@en ;
