    schema:aggregatedRating hptag:Rating2 ;
    schema:author "R. Trebor Scholz" ;
    schema:dateCreated "2023"^^xsd:int ;
    schema:genre hpcom:BookNonFiction ;
    schema:name "Own this!: How platform cooperatives help workers build a democratic Internet" ;
    schema:review "The topic is of great interest to me, however the book never really gets into an exploration of how co-operatives work or what challenges they face. We get lots and lots of examples and mentions without any real takeaways. At times it felt unnecessary to see blockchain mentioned in places without exploring all the other governance mechanisms. Not recommended for reading."@en ;
