    schema:name "Talk Like TED: The 9 Public-Speaking Secrets of the World's Top Minds" ;
    schema:review "I had a presentation coming up, so though this might a good quick read. Worst case scenario, its completely useless and I won't damage my comms skills. The book does have some decent ideas so I've made a note of them for future reference. But could have done without. Recommended if you have no ideas on what ideas could be considered for talking/presentation."@en ;
