    schema:name "The Dip: The Extraordinary Benefits of Knowing When to Quit (and When to Stick)" ;
    schema:review "This is a very small tiny book that really packs a punch. Good simple structure and framework to make sense of should I quit or not. I wrote about it - https://harshp.com/blog/the-dip - and this book gave me the thinking process and allowed me to quit my job (which I had been thinking of anyway)."@en ;
