    schema:description "We compare requirements regarding consent between ISO/IEC TS 27560:2023, ISO/IEC 29184:2020 Privacy Notices, and the GDPR and use the DPV to create interoperable consent records and receipts, and implementation of DGA machine-readable consent forms."@en ;
