    schema:datePublished "2024-11-27T00:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime ;
    schema:description "This article describes the version 2 iteration of the DPV in terms of its contents, methodology, current adoptions and uses, and future potential. It also describes the relevance and role of DPV in acting as a common vocabulary to support various regulatory (e.g., EU's DGA and AI Act) and community initiatives (e.g., Solid) emerging across the globe."@en ;
